<!doctype html>
<html style="color-scheme: light only; supported-color-schemes: light;">
  <head>
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light only" />
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light" />
  </head>
  <body bgcolor="#f6f7f9" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f6f7f9; background-color: #f6f7f9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222;">
    <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 16px;">
      <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e7e7e7; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
        <img src="cid:logo@repairhub" alt="Miami Photography Center" style="display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 640px; height: auto; margin: 0;" />

        <div style="padding: 30px;">
        <h1 style="margin: 0 0 18px 0; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.3; color: #111111;">Service Order Confirmation</h1>

        <p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Dear <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
          Your equipment has been successfully registered under service order <strong>#{{orderCode}}</strong>.
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
          The attached PDF includes the equipment information, requested service details, and order documentation.
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 22px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
          Our technical team will begin the evaluation and service process. You will receive status updates as the order moves through each applicable stage.
        </p>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #ececec; margin: 24px 0;"></div>

        <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666666;">
          For questions regarding your order, service updates, authorization requests, or technical recommendations, contact us at:
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
          <a href="mailto:service@miamiphotographycenter.com" style="color: #0056b3; text-decoration: none;">service@miamiphotographycenter.com</a>
        </p>

        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Thank you for trusting us.</p>

        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
          Best regards,<br />
          <strong>Miami Photography Center</strong><br />
          <span style="color: #0056b3;">Technical Service Department</span>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="padding: 16px 8px 0 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #999999; text-align: center;">
        This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
